This rule focuses on UI elements and Quality of Life features for "FTBKingdoms".

**FTB Teams UI Leverage.**
**Custom Menus (`Screen`, `AbstractContainerScreen`):** Kingdom Menu with tabs (Members, Treasury, Chat, Roles, Rules, Logs, Leaderboards). Data synced via packets.
**Notifications:** Client-side toasts/chat for alerts.
**Citizen Chat:** Custom kingdom chat channel.

**Leaderboards:** Compiled server-side, synced to clients.